Since JAXB 3.0, classes are in package `jakarta.xml.bind`

`javax.xml.bind` was for JAXB until 2.x.

So you must either:
- import classes in package `jakarta.xml.bind` in your source files, if you have control on the dependant classes, but it looks like it&#39;s not the case here.
- or **downgrade the dependency to JAXB 2**:

``` lang-xml
&lt;!-- JAXB 2 --&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;jakarta.xml.bind&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;jakarta.xml.bind-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;2.3.3&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;org.glassfish.jaxb&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;jaxb-runtime&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;2.3.9&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;scope&gt;runtime&lt;/scope&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
```

